<header class="modal-header">
    <h1>转移博客所有权</h1>
</header>
<a class="close icon-x" href="" title="关闭" {{action "closeModal"}}><span class="hidden">关闭</span></a>

<div class="modal-body">
    <p>
        你确定要将此博客的所有权转给其他人吗？此操作是不可逆的。
    </p>
</div>

<div class="modal-footer">
    <button {{action "closeModal"}} class="btn btn-default btn-minor">取消</button>
    {{#gh-spin-button action="confirm" class="btn btn-red" submitting=submitting}}是的，我确定{{/gh-spin-button}}
</div>
